features.name: Inactive Users Query

features.defaultConfiguration:
{
	"condition":"last_session < now() - interval '3600 days'",
	"query":"SELECT * FROM users.users WHERE %s",
	"insert":"INSERT INTO users.users_archive (%s) ON CONFLICT (id) DO UPDATE SET",
	"delete":"DELETE FROM users.users as U USING users.users_archive as D WHERE U.id = D.id",
	"retained_fields":"first_session",
	"schedulingRule":"0 30 8 ? * *"
}

DB Dumper
